text: Breanna Nicole Yde (born June 11, 2003) is an American child actor. She played Frankie Hathaway on the television show The Haunted Hathaways, Tomika on School of Rock, Zoey in the television film Santa Hunters, Akimi in Escape from Mr. Lemoncello's Library, and Gina on the Netflix television show Malibu Rescue. == References == Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Australian actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles
